snippet.description:
n this video, we bring you a unique and mouthwatering recipe, Chicken 65 Idli!  A fusion of South Indian tradition and spicy flavors, this dish combines soft, fluffy idlis with crispy, flavorful fried chicken. Watch as we prepare this innovative recipe in our beautiful village setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional cooking methods.

What‚Äôs special about this recipe?

The perfect blend of soft idlis and spicy Chicken 65.
Simple steps that you can follow to recreate this dish at home.
A wholesome and flavorful meal for all occasions!
Join us for this delicious adventure filled with authentic village vibes.

Sankranthiki Vasthunam is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #venkateshdaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. Touted as an extraordinary triangular crime entertainer, revolving around three characters- the protagonist, his ex-girlfriend, and his excellent wife. Produced by Sri Venkateswara Creations on a massive scale.

Meenakshi Chaudhary and Aishwarya Rajesh are the heroines opposite Venkatesh. Music is composed by Bheems Ceciroleo, Cinematography by Sameer Reddy, Production Designing by A S Prakash.

In the 3rd T20I, Sri Lanka and New Zealand went head-to-head at the Saxton Oval. New Zealand won the toss and asked Sri Lanka to bat first. Sri Lanka posted 218 runs on the board for 5 wickets in their 20 overs. A brilliant 101 runs knock from Kusal Parera helped the Lankans to achieve a huge score. ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: INDIA'S GOT LATENT Bouncer Breaks Character | Dostcast w/ Amin Khan
snippet.description:
Amin Khan is a professional bodyguard and has been a bouncer for 18 years in Mumbai. He was a Maharashtra-level bodybuilder and has provided security to celebrities like Poonam Pandey and Nora Fatehi. He has also acted in movies like Ready with Salman Khan. Currently, he is a bouncer on Samay Raina‚Äôs show India‚Äôs Got Latent.

In this episode, Vinamre and Amin talk about:

‚Ä¢His early days during his bodybuilding career and the consumption of steroids
‚Ä¢The craziest experiences of being a bouncer, Handling crowds in high-pressure situations
‚Ä¢The process of securing VIPs in different scenarios, How celebrities are in real life
‚Ä¢His experience working with Salman Khan in a movie and Amitabh Bachchan in KBC
‚Ä¢The struggles and challenges faced by bouncers, His experiences in dance bars and clubs

Watch this episode to uncover the real-life story of Andrew Tate of India‚Äôs Got Latent.

00:00 - Introduction
0:50 - Who is Amin Khan?
4:40 - Craziest 'India's Got Latent' episode
7:02 - Why are bouncers rude?
